	'You enter a half bathroom with a large sink area and hardwood floors. The toilet sits along the far wall. It all looks very spotless. The main bathroom with the tub and shower must be upstairs, you assume.'
	'You can do your hair and makeup in the <a href="exec:gt ''mirror'', ''start''">mirror</a> above the sink.'
	gs 'din_van', 'prvt_pee'
	act 'Leave the bathroom': gt 'dimaHome','hallway'
end

if $ARGS[0] = 'livingroom':
	*clr & cla
	minut += 1
	gs 'stat'
	'<center><b><font color = maroon>Living room</font></b></center>'
	'<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/resident/dimkahome/livingroom.jpg"></center>'
	'The spacious living room is very clean and tidy. Everything appears perfectly in place, the couch is a large L shape, with shelves set against the back. Several very large windows provide a great view of the manicured lawn. Hanging on the main wall above the fireplace is a huge flat screen TV. You are astonished by how crisp and stylish everything seems. Nothing like your own home.'
	act 'Leave the living room': gt 'dimaHome','hallway'
end

if $ARGS[0] = 'kitchen':
    *clr & cla
    minut += 1
    gs 'stat'
    '<center><b><font color = maroon>Kitchen</font></b></center>'
    '<center><img <<$set_imgh>> src="images/locations/pavlovsk/resident/dimkahome/kitchen.jpg"></center>'
    'You enter the kitchen, finding that it matches the decor and cleanliness of the rest of the home. All the granite and glass surfaces are polished to a reflective gleam. A large chandelier hangs above the kitchen table, while the tiled floor glints in the light.'
!!Dimkas mother will be here 50% of the time from 06:00 to 22:00 on all days but Fridays then from 06:00 to 19:00
	if (hour >= 6 and hour <= 22 and rand (0,1) = 1) or (hour >= 6 and hour <= 19 and week = 5):
		'You see Dimka''s mother Olya is in the kitchen, drinking tea. She is finely dressed with flawless makeup. You don''t think she has noticed you yet.'
		if met_DimkaMother = 0:
			act 'Talk': gt 'dimaHome','kitchen1'
		else
			act 'Talk': gt 'dimaHome','kitchen2'
		end
	end
	act 'Leave the kitchen': gt 'dimaHome','hallway'
end

if $ARGS[0] = 'study':
	cls
	minut += 1
	gs 'stat'
	'<center><h4><font color="maroon">Study</font></h4></center>'
	'<center><img  src="images/locations/pavlovsk/resident/dimkahome/study.jpg"></center>'
	!!make it so there is only a 50% chance he is here even if the hours are correct
	if ((hour >= 18 and week <= 5) or (hour >= 9 and week => 6)) and rand(0,1) = 0:
		if met_DimkaDad = 0:
			'You see Dimka''s father Leonid sitting behind a beautiful polished large wooden desk. He is well dressed and not bad looking, for a older guy. He seems to be working on something, you don''t think he has noticed you yet.'
			if hotcat > 6:
				gt 'dimaHome', 'study1'
			else
				gt 'dimaHome', 'study2'
			end
		elseif met_DimkaDad = 1:
			'You see Dimka''s father Leonid sitting behind a beautiful polished large wooden desk. He is well dressed and not bad looking, for a older guy. He seems to be working on something, you don''t think he has noticed you yet.'
			if hotcat > 6:
				gt 'dimaHome', 'study3'
			else
				gt 'dimaHome', 'study4'
			end
		end
	else
		act 'Leave the study': gt 'dimaHome','hallway'
	end
end

